you aren't too bad yourself.

552
00:25:30,222 --> 00:25:32,781
A perfect relationship consists of
both parties loving each other

553
00:25:33,062 --> 00:25:34,462
as equals.

554
00:25:35,141 --> 00:25:36,822
I hope you can remember my words.

555
00:25:44,982 --> 00:25:46,381
Right after I joined the law firm,

556
00:25:46,421 --> 00:25:47,381
my mentor showed me

557
00:25:47,381 --> 00:25:49,222
dozens of divorce cases in one go.

558
00:25:49,342 --> 00:25:50,462
I doubted my life decisions after that.

559
00:25:50,661 --> 00:25:52,381
Do you think I'll get a brain tumor

560
00:25:52,421 --> 00:25:53,141
just because I see them all day?

561
00:25:53,421 --> 00:25:54,301
Stop talking back.

562
00:25:54,541 --> 00:25:56,781
You just want to tell me
that I will have a divorce,

563
00:25:56,781 --> 00:25:57,301
right?

564
00:25:57,301 --> 00:25:58,261
I didn't say that.

565
00:25:58,862 --> 00:26:00,381
Don't tell me you don't wish
to get married?

566
00:26:00,582 --> 00:26:01,661
Of course I do.

567
00:26:01,982 --> 00:26:03,301
Don't tell me you don't wish
to settle down?

568
00:26:03,661 --> 00:26:04,222
I...

569
00:26:05,501 --> 00:26:08,021
Mainly, my mother likes her too.

570
00:26:08,742 --> 00:26:09,541
She told me not to miss out on

571
00:26:09,541 --> 00:26:10,822
a girl who is

572
00:26:11,021 --> 00:26:12,702
this nice to me.

573
00:26:13,342 --> 00:26:14,381
Will you be nice to her then?

574
00:26:14,541 --> 00:26:15,901
Of course I will.

575
00:26:16,222 --> 00:26:17,462
Will you like her as much

576
00:26:17,622 --> 00:26:18,862
as you like Dong Miaomiao then?

577
00:26:21,661 --> 00:26:22,742
Love can be cultivated.

578
00:26:22,942 --> 00:26:23,901
I don't believe you.

579
00:26:24,421 --> 00:26:25,301
I couldn't care less.

580
00:26:25,342 --> 00:26:26,102
Hurry up.

581
00:26:31,060 --> 00:26:33,900
(Bliss)

582
00:26:37,181 --> 00:26:38,342
Hey.

583
00:26:38,342 --> 00:26:40,021
You're getting married tomorrow,

584
00:26:40,021 --> 00:26:43,181
yet Ning Zhiqian isn't here
to help you out?

585
00:26:43,501 --> 00:26:45,222
He's at the hospital.
He's busy with his work.

586
00:26:45,742 --> 00:26:47,702
I sure hope he won't be busy tomorrow.

587
00:26:51,381 --> 00:26:52,261
Done!

588
00:26:56,141 --> 00:26:57,381
Mrs. Ning.

589
00:26:59,661 --> 00:27:01,342
Let me tell you something.

590
00:27:02,222 --> 00:27:05,021
Lately, a patient's relative

591
00:27:05,021 --> 00:27:06,222
has been courting me.

592
00:27:06,261 --> 00:27:07,661
His name is Jiang Cheng.

593
00:27:08,021 --> 00:27:09,661
What does he look like?
Do you have a picture of him? Show me.

594
00:27:09,982 --> 00:27:12,702
He's very cute.

595
00:27:12,742 --> 00:27:15,062
He's just like Monchhichi.

596
00:27:15,062 --> 00:27:16,342
And, I can tell

597
00:27:16,342 --> 00:27:18,462
he's a househusband.

598
00:27:18,501 --> 00:27:20,021
He calls me every day.

599
00:27:20,062 --> 00:27:22,501
He buys flowers for me
whenever he comes to the hospital.

600
00:27:22,501 --> 00:27:24,421
He also buys snacks for me.

601
00:27:25,582 --> 00:27:26,421
Seems like

602
00:27:26,421 --> 00:27:27,862
you've fallen for him.

603
00:27:30,102 --> 00:27:30,702
You know?

604
00:27:30,702 --> 00:27:32,141
One time, during my night shift,

605
00:27:32,141 --> 00:27:33,381
I was especially hungry.

606
00:27:33,381 --> 00:27:34,901
I wanted to have some garlic crayfish.

607
00:27:34,901 --> 00:27:35,982
Guess what happened?

608
00:27:37,462 --> 00:27:40,102
Did he order crayfish for you?

609
00:27:40,301 --> 00:27:42,901
He drove to the hospital
and delivered it to me personally.

610
00:27:42,901 --> 00:27:44,661
He delivered it all the way
to the duty office.

611
00:27:44,661 --> 00:27:45,982
He even peeled them for me.

612
00:27:45,982 --> 00:27:48,261
It would've been perfect if he fed me.

613
00:27:48,942 --> 00:27:50,222
He's that considerate?

614
00:27:57,541 --> 00:28:00,141
If you wish to get married that badly,

615
00:28:00,622 --> 00:28:03,102
I'll toss the bouquet to you tomorrow.

616
00:28:03,582 --> 00:28:05,181
Who said I wanted to get married?

617
00:28:06,102 --> 00:28:07,381
If you want to toss it to me,

618
00:28:07,381 --> 00:28:08,742
you better aim it properly.

619
00:28:10,661 --> 00:28:11,421
I shall be accurate with my aim.

620
00:28:14,381 --> 00:28:16,021
How dare you throw that at me?

621
00:28:16,021 --> 00:28:17,541
How dare you?

622
00:28:28,822 --> 00:28:29,381
Hello?

623
00:28:29,822 --> 00:28:30,742
I just got off work.

624
00:28:31,222 --> 00:28:32,222
It must've been tough on you.

625
00:28:32,501 --> 00:28:33,301
Not at all.

626
00:28:33,982 --> 00:28:35,661
Rest early then. See you tomorrow.

627
00:28:36,462 --> 00:28:37,421
So, tomorrow...

628
00:29:09,400 --> 00:29:12,280
(Don't you think he's treating you
as my replacement?)

629
00:29:14,181 --> 00:29:15,982
In an unequal relationship,

630
00:29:16,062 --> 00:29:19,622
the person who devotes herself
to the other will be hurt the most.

631
00:29:20,520 --> 00:29:24,210
(A perfect relationship consists of
both parties loving each other)

632
00:29:24,240 --> 00:29:25,640
(as equals.)

633
00:29:43,330 --> 00:29:45,330
(Dear John University School
of Medicine,)

634
00:29:45,342 --> 00:29:46,462
(this is Ruan Liuzheng.)

635
00:29:47,090 --> 00:29:48,570
(After careful consideration,)

636
00:29:48,582 --> 00:29:50,381
(I decided to give up
on the opportunity)

637
00:29:50,381 --> 00:29:51,622
(to study for a Master's degree.)

638
00:29:52,090 --> 00:29:54,050
(Thank you for the opportunity.)

639
00:30:09,501 --> 00:30:10,622
Liuzheng.

640
00:30:12,501 --> 00:30:13,541
Where is she?

641
00:30:16,582 --> 00:30:17,622
Jianzhong,

642
00:30:18,102 --> 00:30:19,742
did you see our daughter?

643
00:30:20,261 --> 00:30:21,702
What's the matter? I didn't see her.

644
00:30:21,862 --> 00:30:22,862
Where did she go?

645
00:30:22,901 --> 00:30:24,021
Liuzheng?

646
00:30:24,181 --> 00:30:25,141
Liuzheng!

647
00:30:25,222 --> 00:30:27,781
Mom, why are you shouting
this early in the morning?

648
00:30:28,342 --> 00:30:29,781
Your sister is missing!

649
00:30:34,541 --> 00:30:35,541
Is she a runaway bride?

650
00:30:37,021 --> 00:30:37,982
That's pretty cool.

651
00:30:40,901 --> 00:30:42,582
Mister, can you drive faster?

652
00:30:42,582 --> 00:30:43,862
What time is your flight?

653
00:30:43,862 --> 00:30:44,622
8am.

654
00:30:45,062 --> 00:30:46,062
Alright, sit tight.

655
00:30:52,700 --> 00:30:56,700
(Entrance)

656
00:30:58,102 --> 00:30:58,942
Dong!

657
00:30:59,541 --> 00:31:00,342
Dong.

658
00:31:00,901 --> 00:31:01,622
Liuzheng?

659
00:31:02,862 --> 00:31:04,541
Right now, we don't love each other
deeply,

660
00:31:04,541 --> 00:31:05,661
and we're not equals.

661
00:31:06,181 --> 00:31:07,462
However, perfect love

662
00:31:07,582 --> 00:31:09,062
doesn't exist in this world.

663
00:31:09,742 --> 00:31:11,541
I might not be his best choice,

664
00:31:12,342 --> 00:31:14,141
but I will do all I can to love him.

665
00:31:14,742 --> 00:31:16,261
I will make sure he falls for me.

666
00:31:16,702 --> 00:31:17,982
We will definitely be happy.

667
00:31:19,301 --> 00:31:20,102
Goodbye, Dong.

668
00:31:20,102 --> 00:31:20,982
Safe trip ahead.

669
00:31:47,260 --> 00:31:50,580
♪White clouds will never♪

670
00:31:50,580 --> 00:31:54,300
♪Miss out on clear skies♪

671
00:31:55,500 --> 00:31:57,780
♪As we waited♪

672
00:31:57,780 --> 00:32:02,020
♪We deserve the embrace♪

673
00:32:02,060 --> 00:32:06,820
♪However, we never♪

674
00:32:06,820 --> 00:32:10,620
♪Chose to stay♪

675
00:32:10,620 --> 00:32:14,340
♪We only care about the future♪

676
00:32:14,340 --> 00:32:21,500
♪While the present slips past us♪

677
00:32:25,140 --> 00:32:27,020
♪Before choosing a direction♪

678
00:32:27,020 --> 00:32:29,420
♪At the next crossroad♪

679
00:32:29,420 --> 00:32:32,900
♪I let go of your hand out of habit♪

680
00:32:32,900 --> 00:32:37,020
♪Two hearts anticipate
approaching each other♪

681
00:32:37,020 --> 00:32:41,540
♪Yet suffer in regrets♪

682
00:32:41,540 --> 00:32:43,380
♪Choosing a direction♪

683
00:32:43,380 --> 00:32:45,740
♪At the next crossroad♪

684
00:32:45,740 --> 00:32:49,220
♪Is like tearing the universe apart♪

685
00:32:49,220 --> 00:32:53,260
♪Losing oneself in regret♪

686
00:32:53,260 --> 00:32:58,260
♪Saving oneself with silence♪

687
00:33:00,740 --> 00:33:04,980
♪That won't do♪

688
00:33:04,980 --> 00:33:06,860
(2019 Beiya Hospital, Jiangzhou, China)

689
00:33:06,862 --> 00:33:08,462
Thank you, my dear.

690
00:33:14,342 --> 00:33:15,421
I thought you were Tan Ya.

691
00:33:16,102 --> 00:33:16,982
Thank you, Mr. Ning.

692
00:33:17,181 --> 00:33:18,901
You have 15 minutes for the meal.

693
00:33:20,982 --> 00:33:21,582
What's wrong?

694
00:33:22,261 --> 00:33:23,541
Attend outpatient duty with me
this afternoon.

695
00:33:24,301 --> 00:33:25,381
Me?

696
00:33:34,822 --> 00:33:35,661
You have two minutes left.

697
00:33:35,702 --> 00:33:36,982
You can go to the restroom first.

698
00:33:37,141 --> 00:33:38,622
That's fine. I don't feel like going.

699
00:33:38,742 --> 00:33:39,822
Don't drink too much water.

700
00:33:39,982 --> 00:33:40,702
Why?

701
00:33:40,942 --> 00:33:42,062
You won't have time to use the restroom.

702
00:33:43,181 --> 00:33:45,421
It's not like I haven't done this
in West District Hospital before.

703
00:33:45,421 --> 00:33:46,982
It's different here.

704
00:33:47,742 --> 00:33:49,381
I suggest you prepare
some adult diapers.

705
00:33:50,982 --> 00:33:51,901
Do you need them?

706
00:33:54,381 --> 00:33:55,062
Dr. Ning is here.

707
00:33:55,541 --> 00:33:56,181
Doctor.

708
00:33:56,181 --> 00:33:56,582
Dr. Ning.

709
00:33:56,582 --> 00:33:57,261
Please wait here.

710
00:34:01,301 --> 00:34:02,261
Dr. Wu,

711
00:34:02,342 --> 00:34:03,501
where did Mr. Ning go?

712
00:34:04,181 --> 00:34:05,421
He's performing outpatient duty
with his new student.

713
00:34:07,942 --> 00:34:08,981
New student?

714
00:34:09,622 --> 00:34:10,422
Who is it?

715
00:34:10,662 --> 00:34:11,662
Of course it's Dr. Ruan.

716
00:34:11,701 --> 00:34:12,941
Mr. Ning actually took her in?

717
00:34:14,701 --> 00:34:16,221
There are four steps to becoming
Mr. Ning's student.

718
00:34:16,301 --> 00:34:18,382
Doing chores, performing outpatient
duty, and performing surgeries.

719
00:34:18,382 --> 00:34:19,501
That's what I went through.

720
00:34:20,622 --> 00:34:23,062
Doing chores, performing outpatient
duty, and performing surgeries?

721
00:34:23,822 --> 00:34:24,981
What's the fourth step then?

722
00:34:26,261 --> 00:34:26,862
Take a guess.

723
00:34:27,062 --> 00:34:27,862
Take a guess?

724
00:34:28,501 --> 00:34:29,461
Forget it.

725
00:34:29,622 --> 00:34:30,582
I'll have them myself.

726
00:34:32,021 --> 00:34:33,342
Dr. Ding, you bought a lot of food.

727
00:34:33,382 --> 00:34:34,021
Did you buy my share too?

728
00:34:34,062 --> 00:34:35,142
Yeah, join me.

729
00:34:35,142 --> 00:34:36,261
- Coming.
- Come and join me.

730
00:34:37,221 --> 00:34:38,301
Come on. Let's eat.

731
00:34:38,780 --> 00:34:41,460
(Beiya Hospital, Ning Zhiqian)

732
00:34:42,541 --> 00:34:43,221
You can call their numbers now.

733
00:34:43,261 --> 00:34:43,920
Okay.

734
00:34:43,920 --> 00:34:44,540
(Beiya Hospital, Ning Zhiqian)

735
00:34:45,741 --> 00:34:46,422
I'm the first patient!

736
00:34:46,422 --> 00:34:48,021
Wait!

737
00:34:48,062 --> 00:34:49,142
Please line up.

738
00:34:49,422 --> 00:34:51,062
What's going on? Please keep quiet.

739
00:34:55,501 --> 00:34:56,662
Your recovery is going pretty well.

740
00:34:56,662 --> 00:34:57,541
Is that so?

741
00:34:58,182 --> 00:34:59,021
There's no issue here.

742
00:34:59,182 --> 00:34:59,902
Remember, come back

743
00:34:59,902 --> 00:35:01,461
for a checkup once every month.

744
00:35:02,021 --> 00:35:04,822
I feel like I'm becoming
more and more forgetful.

745
00:35:04,822 --> 00:35:06,781
Is this because of

746
00:35:07,701 --> 00:35:08,781
the side effect?

747
00:35:09,021 --> 00:35:10,662
No, this is normal.

748
00:35:10,662 --> 00:35:12,142
Do not be stressed out by it.

749
00:35:12,142 --> 00:35:12,941
Take your medicine on time.

750
00:35:12,981 --> 00:35:13,622
Next.

751
00:35:13,622 --> 00:35:14,582
Take your medical record with you.

752
00:35:14,862 --> 00:35:15,501
Okay.

753
00:35:16,422 --> 00:35:17,981
My head hurts lately.

754
00:35:17,981 --> 00:35:19,301
I can't sleep at night.

755
00:35:19,301 --> 00:35:21,182
And, my vision is blurry at night.

756
00:35:21,261 --> 00:35:22,662
Blurry vision?

757
00:35:22,941 --> 00:35:24,062
Remove your glasses.

758
00:35:26,701 --> 00:35:27,981
Look into my eyes.

759
00:35:28,021 --> 00:35:28,981
Can you see my fingers?

760
00:35:29,021 --> 00:35:29,781
I can.

761
00:35:30,182 --> 00:35:31,342
It's not a big issue then.

762
00:35:31,902 --> 00:35:33,102
Did you go for plastic surgery lately?

763
00:35:33,461 --> 00:35:35,142
You're a neurosurgeon, right?

764
00:35:35,142 --> 00:35:37,261
I don't think you should
interfere with my personal life.

765
00:35:37,261 --> 00:35:38,261
You have to tell the doctor

766
00:35:38,261 --> 00:35:39,501
about what you've done lately.

767
00:35:39,541 --> 00:35:41,142
Only then, he'll be able to
give you an accurate diagnosis.

768
00:35:41,902 --> 00:35:43,062
Mister, where do you feel uncomfortable?

769
00:35:44,501 --> 00:35:47,422
I feel dizzy and bloated.

770
00:35:47,541 --> 00:35:48,382
Does your head hurt then?

771
00:35:48,461 --> 00:35:49,182
Yeah, it hurts.

772
00:35:49,301 --> 00:35:51,182
Straighten your arms for me.

773
00:35:53,701 --> 00:35:55,541
Mister, please stand up.

774
00:35:55,822 --> 00:35:56,781
Slowly.

775
00:35:58,021 --> 00:35:59,422
Do some steps for me.

776
00:36:04,541 --> 00:36:05,461
Alright.

777
00:36:05,501 --> 00:36:06,221
Mister, sit down.

778
00:36:07,822 --> 00:36:09,902
This might be peripheral neuropathy.

779
00:36:10,062 --> 00:36:11,102
I'll give you a...

780
00:36:11,142 --> 00:36:12,301
Doctor, what did you say just now?

781
00:36:12,662 --> 00:36:14,021
I have peripheral neuropathy?

782
00:36:14,062 --> 00:36:14,862
Yes, that's what I suspect.

783
00:36:15,182 --> 00:36:16,382
Please go for an X-ray scan first.

784
00:36:16,382 --> 00:36:18,062
I'll give you a prescription later.

785
00:36:27,221 --> 00:36:28,741
Judging from the image,
it doesn't look like a huge issue.

786
00:36:29,662 --> 00:36:30,981
You may opt for conservative treatment.

787
00:36:31,941 --> 00:36:32,382
Next.

788
00:36:34,862 --> 00:36:35,501
Doctor, I think the surgery

789
00:36:35,501 --> 00:36:37,541
wasn't done cleanly.

790
00:36:37,541 --> 00:36:38,941
I think it wasn't removed entirely.

791
00:36:39,582 --> 00:36:40,461
It looks pretty clean to me.

792
00:36:40,902 --> 00:36:43,021
Do you have a better X-ray scan here?

793
00:36:43,142 --> 00:36:45,261
It's best if you can
scan his entire body.

794
00:36:45,541 --> 00:36:46,541
The cost doesn't matter.

795
00:36:46,541 --> 00:36:47,822
Give us the costliest treatment.

796
00:36:53,662 --> 00:36:54,382
His name is Ning Zhiqian.

797
00:36:54,382 --> 00:36:55,662
Doctor!

798
00:36:55,781 --> 00:36:57,422
I traveled for over two hours

799
00:36:57,422 --> 00:36:58,182
just to come here.

800
00:36:58,182 --> 00:36:59,021
Doctor, please register
my number for me.

801
00:36:59,021 --> 00:37:00,902
Can you register a number for me?

802
00:37:00,902 --> 00:37:02,382
Please wait here.

803
00:37:02,382 --> 00:37:03,701
Sorry for the trouble.

804
00:37:03,701 --> 00:37:04,582
Doctor,

805
00:37:04,582 --> 00:37:06,422
this illness of mine
is killing me.

806
00:37:06,461 --> 00:37:07,182
Please take a look.

807
00:37:17,182 --> 00:37:18,741
Doctor, please help us out.

808
00:37:18,822 --> 00:37:20,461
It won't take you too long
to register a number for us.

809
00:37:20,461 --> 00:37:21,221
Yeah, I'm begging you here.

810
00:37:21,221 --> 00:37:22,701
Please.

811
00:37:22,741 --> 00:37:24,541
My illness is killing me.

812
00:37:24,902 --> 00:37:25,981
Ran,

813
00:37:26,102 --> 00:37:26,981
Mr. Ning is still around, right?

814
00:37:26,981 --> 00:37:28,221
Register their numbers for them.

815
00:37:28,221 --> 00:37:28,981
Alright, I got it.

816
00:37:29,102 --> 00:37:30,342
Register a number for me too.

817
00:37:30,342 --> 00:37:30,981
Over here.

818
00:37:32,221 --> 00:37:32,701
Over here.

819
00:37:34,741 --> 00:37:36,221
I was right to tell you
not to drink too much, right?

820
00:37:40,301 --> 00:37:41,301
Pack your things and get ready to leave.

821
00:37:41,461 --> 00:37:43,021
I don't think we can leave yet.

822
00:37:43,021 --> 00:37:44,261
I might need to take up
some of your time.

823
00:37:44,622 --> 00:37:45,021
What's wrong?

824
00:37:45,021 --> 00:37:46,781
Two patients didn't register
their numbers in time.

